{"tid":1334934,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"賴冠霖單方面向CUBE娛樂提出解約：希望單獨活動","createTime":"2019-07-20T10:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T09:10:17.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c50b13ac2483beea061d69121543fa3438068c","tid":1334934,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"從南韓團體Wanna One發跡的賴冠霖驚傳主動提出和經紀公司解約，根據韓媒報導，賴冠霖單方面向CUBE娛樂提出合約無效，希望能獨自活動。公司已證實消息屬實，表示收到賴冠霖提出的解約內容證明，會在稍後發表立場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4089/d4089254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4089%2Fd4089254.jpg&h=ce8f1774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲賴冠霖無預警提出解約。（圖／翻攝自賴冠霖微博）<br />\n<br />\n根據南韓媒體《spotvnews》報導，賴冠霖向CUBE娛樂公司單方面告知要解除合約，提出了解約的「內容證明書」，根據相關人士透露，「賴冠霖向CUBE娛樂通報了合約終止的內容證明，希望未來能獨立活動。」<br />\n<br />\nCUBE娛樂也向《spotvnews》證實消息屬實，「確實收到了賴冠霖送來的內容證明，將會在稍後發表正式官方立場。」<br />\n<br />\n賴冠霖2017年以CUBE娛樂練習生之姿，參加選秀節目《Produce 101》第二季，後來人氣高漲，順利入選成為Wanna One的一員。雖然Wanna One團體合作已到期，成員們皆分道揚鑣，賴冠霖一邊參與大陸的活動，前陣子還和師兄PENTAGON的禹奭組成「禹奭X冠霖」雙人組合闖蕩歌壇，突然要求解約，令粉絲感到衝擊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4105/d4105597.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4105%2Fd4105597.jpg&h=c0c38343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲賴冠霖之前還來台舉辦見面會。（圖／記者張一中攝）<br />\n<br />\n而這也是Wanna One成員第二名與所屬公司鬧出合約紛爭。Wanna One第一名入選的人氣王「姜丹尼爾」，才因為合約問題與公司對簿公堂，日前終於塵埃落定，他成立一人經紀公司，也宣布會在新加坡與香港舉辦粉絲見面會。而現在賴冠霖也爆出要解約，更讓資深粉絲想到當年EXO中國籍成員接連單方面提出解約，一個個離開的悲慘回憶。<br />\n<br />\n中國人黎講嘎嘎最高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4b4524a5d5919b2170d75feb60fdbc508c4a3c","tid":1334934,"uid":68678,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:07:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">25狗賴屎霖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"0c4173f67dae21d8653dd9e4eef880b140fd08cb","tid":1334934,"uid":238483,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"@Swag <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomo