 />"},{"pid":"58938f8809dae9213ff000296feab714f13dec9b","tid":1334934,"uid":91230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"97885231a0b46be570950272a21ed89d917bff4d","tid":1334934,"uid":201752,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7xss0c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7xss0c.png&h=21ee231e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機都用殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那人回歸支那 不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"佢中國人嚟 唔好怪佢"},{"pid":"f502802945a421ed5c83f82dc235e0e9d948a3d1","tid":1334934,"uid":279888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:13:28.000Z","msg":"佢唔會真係覺得自己solo紅得起啊麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a358588ae33d5ffd79d20f38700860593012908","tid":1334934,"uid":253373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8c50b13ac2483beea061d69121543fa3438068c","tid":1334934,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"從南韓團體Wanna One發跡的賴冠霖驚傳主動提出和經紀公司解約，根據韓媒報導，賴冠霖單方面向CUBE娛樂提出合約無效，希望能獨自活動。公司已證實消息屬實，表示收到賴冠霖提出的解約內容證明，會在稍後發表立場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4089/d4089254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4089%2Fd4089254.jpg&h=ce8f1774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲賴冠霖無預警提出解約。（圖／翻攝自賴冠霖微博）<br />\n<br />\n根據南韓媒體《spotvnews》報導，賴冠霖向CUBE娛樂公司單方面告知要解除合約，提出了解約的「內容證明書」，根據相關人士透露，「賴冠霖向CUBE娛樂通報了合約終止的內容證明，希望未來能獨立活動。」<br />\n<br />\nCUBE娛樂也向《spotvnews》證實消息屬實，「確實收到了賴冠霖送來的內容證明，將會在稍後發表正式官方立場。」<br />\n<br />\n賴冠霖2017年以CUBE娛樂練習生之姿，參加選秀節目《Produce 101》第二季，後來人氣高漲，順利入選成為Wanna One的一員。雖然Wanna One團體合作已到期，成員們皆分道揚鑣，賴冠霖一邊參與大陸的活動，前陣子還和師兄PENTAGON的禹奭組成「禹奭X冠霖」雙人組合闖蕩歌壇，突然要求解約，令粉絲感到衝擊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4105/d4105597.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4105%2Fd4105597.jpg&h=c0c38343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲賴冠霖之前還來台舉辦見面會。（圖／記者張一中攝）<br />\n<br />\n而這也是Wanna One成員第二名與所屬公司鬧出合約紛爭。Wanna One第一名入選的人氣王「姜丹尼爾」，才因為合約問題與公司對簿公堂，日前終於塵埃落定，他成立一人經紀公司，也宣布會在新加坡與香港舉辦粉絲見面會。而現在賴冠霖也爆出要解約，更讓資深粉絲想到當年EXO中國籍成員接連單方面提出解約，一個個離開的悲慘回憶。<br />\n<br />\n中國人黎講嘎嘎最高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:37:52.000Z","msg":"預左啦，仲留係韓國同你捱咩<br />\n話時話，可唔可以唔好貼佢張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b409a1ced0ad4e768ec79dff6a65ffa862a688e3","tid":1334934,"uid":264433,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:42:10.000Z","msg":"屌大陸仔指定動作 茶蛋嗰三件已經係人版"},{"pid":"b20a990c4c11c6b7abec714c39d6100023851fbd","tid":1334934,"uid":240447,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b409a1ced0ad4e768ec79dff6a65ffa862a688e3","tid":1334934,"uid":264433,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:42:10.000Z","msg":"屌大陸仔指定動作 茶蛋嗰三件已經係人版"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"4件先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db09c7a2839cf31d71d1421b8853ec8ae862c94","tid":1334934,"uid":222742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"Ugly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}